			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	Do you consider yourself a persuasive person?&nbsp; Do you enjoy educating others?&nbsp; Do you want to feel rewarded for your actions?&nbsp; If you answered yes to these, then working with Curebit as a Brand Ambassador is a good opportunity.&nbsp; You&rsquo;ll get into a start-up at ground level and help grow sales and gain traction.&nbsp; Your day will be spent primarily doing outreach to potential clients and explaining our system, getting them onto an education program to learn more about Curebit, then following up to launch a campaign.&nbsp; Essentially, you&rsquo;ll be give some target companies and will get rewarded with a commission each time one signs up.&nbsp; We will then launch the client and get them into a campaign.&nbsp; You&rsquo;ll be able to experience the full spectrum of a SaaS business.</p>
<p>
	&bull; Identify qualified sales prospects and initiate contact<br />
	&bull; Generate your own leads<br />
	&bull; Demo our software to prospective clients<br />
	&bull; Understand prospects&#39; needs and prepare presentations and proposals<br />
	&bull; Close your deals and hit revenue targets<br />
	&bull; Assist in results discovery and creating training materials</p>
<p>
	Skils:</p>
<p>
