<p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	About Curebit:</p>
<p>
	Curebit is the leading social referral platform used by many major online retailers as well as thousands of small ecommerce properties.&nbsp; In other words, we make social media work as an advertising channel by monetizing word of mouth in a tangible and deeply analytical way.&nbsp; Our customers LOVE us because we help them grow sales by leveraging their most valuable asset: their customers! We&rsquo;re rapidly expanding our entire team and opening a Boston office.</p>
